he perpetual contract's deviation from the BLUR spot price across major exchanges. The platform's off-chain order book with on-chain settlement allows for precise rate calculations without typical AMM slippage. Funding payments occur every hour, with rates automatically deducted from trader balances. The rollup architecture enables faster settlement compared to mainnet-based competitors."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
